title: Dakota Johnson Can't Stop Laughing During This Fifty Shades Scene
text:
Dakota Johnson Can't Stop Laughing During This Fifty Shades Scene 
She laughs so hard she cries, actually. Getty By Alyssa Bailey Feb 1, 2017 What happens when Tonight Show improv whiz Dakota Johnson tries out the show's Mad Lib Theater game? She gives the most random words to use in the Fifty Shades interview scene script, then struggles to perform it. She and Jimmy Fallon, who play Anastasia Steele and Christian Grey, really, really cannot keep a straight face between the Beyonc√© and hairless sausage references. Johnson laughs so much she actually does cry.
